model

Class Notebook

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Notebook
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Notebook
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class initializes a Notebook Object which contains information regarding the Notebook's directory, the name of the file, and the name of the Notebook. It also contains a HashMap which maps the name of the Section to the Section object
    Author:
    Michael Tuohy, Trevor Freudig, Alexander Thompson, Scott LaFerriere
    See Also:
